I wish you didn't see that.

753
01:28:44,520 --> 01:28:46,680
就像我之前听你告诉你儿子的一样
It's just like I heard you tell your boy before.

754
01:28:47,700 --> 01:28:48,720
我没有撒谎
Ain't that I lied,

755
01:28:49,780 --> 01:28:51,840
我只是没告诉你全部真相
I just never told you the whole truth.

756
01:28:53,180 --> 01:28:54,620
你根本不是警察
Was you law at all?

757
01:28:55,420 --> 01:28:57,740
伍兹郡的治安官 就如我所说
Sheriff of woods county, just like I said.

758
01:28:59,180 --> 01:29:02,440
我和我的副手们在春天和凯彻姆签约
Me and my deputies, we signed on with ketchum back in the spring.

759
01:29:04,060 --> 01:29:05,680
我们必须接受他们的指挥
We had to take their brand.

760
01:29:07,060 --> 01:29:08,480
和他们一起做些事
Done a few jobs with'em.

761
01:29:08,720 --> 01:29:11,680
但我们发现他们打算在最后一次行动中杀了我们
But we figured out they was planning to gun us down on this last go.

762
01:29:13,290 --> 01:29:15,220
所以我们想先下手为强
So we tried to beat'em to the punch.

763
01:29:15,500 --> 01:29:17,760
失败后 他们一直在追捕我
Took off, and they plugged me from a distance.

764
01:29:20,030 --> 01:29:21,820
他们会追我到天涯海角
They'd have hunted me to the end of the earth.

765
01:29:24,360 --> 01:29:26,040
很抱歉 我最后到了这里
I'm sorry I ended up here.

766
01:29:27,880 --> 01:29:30,180
你想要的真相 是我最不愿做的事
Last thing I wanted, you wanna know the truth of it.

767
01:29:32,660 --> 01:29:34,200
因为那时你对我很好
'Cause you were good to me back then.

768
01:29:34,980 --> 01:29:35,740
呵
Huh.

769
01:29:36,560 --> 01:29:38,840
我永远不会相信你做了他们说的那些事
I could never square you done the things they said.

770
01:29:40,350 --> 01:29:42,500
虽然我现在确实可以相信
Though I sure as hell can believe it now.

771
01:29:52,800 --> 01:29:54,760
我甚至不记得你了
I don't even remember you.

772
01:29:55,930 --> 01:29:59,400
为什么要记得 我只是个农场工人
Well, why would you? I was just a ranch hand.

773
01:30:00,700 --> 01:30:03,080
现在我要成为杀死比利小子的人了
Now I get to be the man who killed Billy the kid.

774
01:30:17,320 --> 01:30:19,220
-坚持住 我去找医生 -不
-You hold on, I'll get the doc. -No.

775
01:30:21,340 --> 01:30:22,190
爸爸
Pa.

776
01:30:22,230 --> 01:30:24,460
我能走到今天是个奇迹
It's a miracle I made it this far.

777
01:30:27,820 --> 01:30:29,240
一旦这消息传出
Once this gets out...

778
01:30:30,500 --> 01:30:32,540
你会听到一些关于我的事
You gonna hear some things about me.

779
01:30:33,640 --> 01:30:34,970
有些是真的
Some of it's true.

780
01:30:36,060 --> 01:30:37,340
但很多都不是
A lot of it ain't.

781
01:30:39,020 --> 01:30:40,140
实际上
Fact is...

782
01:30:42,380 --> 01:30:45,820
我甚至都不知道我是谁或是什么了
I don't even know who or what I was anymore.

783
01:30:49,320 --> 01:30:51,120
我不相信救赎
I don't believe in redemption.

784
01:30:53,360 --> 01:30:56,060
但一个男人可以找到一些慰藉
But a man can find some kind of solace...

785
01:30:57,940 --> 01:31:00,400
如果他有你这样的孩子要抚养
If he's got a boy like you to raise.

786
01:31:03,140 --> 01:31:04,700
世界正在发生变化
The world is changing.

787
01:31:06,900 --> 01:31:08,240
你去看看吧
You go see it.

788
01:31:09,780 --> 01:31:12,680
这里不再是属于我的地方
It's a place I don't belong in no more.

789
01:31:16,320 --> 01:31:17,560
我希望
I'm hoping...

790
01:31:19,200 --> 01:31:20,340
你喜欢
You do.

791
